# Pacman
![Imagem Jogo](data:image/png;base64,)


## Requirements

- ### Python 3.10+

&nbsp;

## How to configure

### 0. (Optional) Virtual Env

```sh
python -m venv env
env/Scripts/activate
```

### 1. Current Environment

```sh
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

&nbsp;

## How to start

```sh
python main.py
```
